Homework4:  Projections and Navigation Assignment
/*
 *  Homework #4
 *
 *  Demonstrates how to draw objects in 3D.
 *  orthogonal & prespective projections & first person view
 *
 *  Key bindings:
 *  1/2/3      Toggle between orthogonal perspective, and first person view
 *  r          Toggle axes
 *  arrows     Change view angle
 *  0          Reset view angle
 *  First Person View
 *  w          Forward
 *  a          Left
 *  s          Backward
 *  d          Right
 *  q          Rotate Left
 *  e          Rotate Right
 *  ESC        Exit
 */

Time to Complete: ~4h